      &lt;img alt="The Instagram camera icon on a pink, blue, and black background" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qUskc8fFgzSJ0yzjkJ2jSACbfSU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73512545/acastro_STK070__02.0.jpg" /&gt;
